		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BASIC CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move rod:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad or Left Analog stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Cast:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Left Analog Stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Reel (rotate stick):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Right Analog Stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Make selection / select item / Advance to next screen / Cast:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X or R3 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Return to previous screen (not available on some screens) / Cast:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Release / Toggle selection screens:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1/L2/R1/R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">FISHING ROD CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Choose item:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Control reel:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Reel</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Operate power gauge:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Make selection / Select item / Advance to next screen / Operate Power Gauge:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Return to previous screen:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Choose mode, lake, etc. / Move, control rod:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Center Stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Release / Toggle selection screens:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1/L2/R1/R2 Button</font><br><br>
        &nbsp;</td>
	 </tr>
	</table>
