		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Unlock 'Free Credits' Play -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Below is the task to complete in order to unlock the bonus feature "Free Credits". This simply means that the arcade core of the game is removed with the ability to Continue after time runs out an infinite number of times. Consider this an 'Unlimited Lives' cheat. To access this once unlocked simply head to Options in main menu and change Credit value to 'Free'.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Free Credit Mode -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Complete all six World Monsters levels and the bonus China World Monsters level</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Kitaura Lake -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Catch 100 Fish</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Yamanaka Lake -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Catch 150 Fish</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Brazil -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Complete USA, Japan, and Comoros World Monsters levels</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock China -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Complete all six World Monsters levels</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Egypt -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Complete USA, Japan, and Comoros World Monsters levels</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock UK -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Complete USA, Japan, and Comoros World Monsters levels</font>&nbsp;<br>
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ACTION REPLAY CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Enable code -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>D00177BA 1040<br>800177BA 1000<br>D0017A6C 60A7<br>80017A6C 5EBC<br>D0017EF6 1040<br>80017EF6 1000</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlimited credits -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>800BDDF8 0009</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Large Fish / Monster -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>80121332 270F<br>80128C90 22B8<br>80128C92 270F</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
